title: Bug 116564 - The title of hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options", but it changes with settings.
OB: When clicking on "OK" and reopening the hyperlink builder, the actual result is that its title becomes "www.actuate.com".
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options", but it changes based on settings.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Click on "OK". 2. Reopen the hyperlink builder. The expected result is that the title of the hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options".
